  body
    #wrap
      .container.marketing
        h1 About Snack Dashboard
        p.marketing-byline What is this all about...
          
        #contentdiv.row-fluid
          .span4.well
            img.marketing-img(src="images/ohmage-logo.png", alt="logo")
            p The snack dataset was collected by participating students from 
              a(href="http://home.lausd.net/") LAUSD 
              | in 2012. They used mobile phones with the 
              a(href="http://www.ohmage.org") Ohmage software
              | .
             
          .span4.well
            img.marketing-img(src="images/mobilize-logo.png", alt="logo")
            p The 
              a(href="http://www.mobilizingcs.org/") Mobilize project 
              | introduces concepts like learning from data, statistics and visualization in a playful and engaging way.

          .span4.well
            img.marketing-img(src="images/opencpu-logo.png", alt="logo") 
            p The 
              a(href="./") Dashboard 
              | allows for visual exploration of the data without the need for advanced software. It is best viewed in Google Chrome.

        iframe#snackvideo(src="//www.youtube.com/embed/9FrB2xu0ghY?enablejsapi=1&autoplay=0&rel=0&modestbranding=1&showinfo=0&showsearch=0")


        hr.soften
        .row-fluid            
          .span4
            h2 Snack Survey

            #myCarousel.carousel.slide
             .carousel-inner
               .active.item
                 img(src="images/survey1.png", alt="snack survey question")
               .item
