               .item
                 img(src="images/survey7.png", alt="snack survey question")
               .item
                 img(src="images/survey8.png", alt="snack survey question")
               .item
                 img(src="images/survey9.png", alt="snack survey question")                                     
             a.carousel-control.left(href='#myCarousel', data-slide='prev') ‹
             a.carousel-control.right(href='#myCarousel', data-slide='next') ›

          .span4#datatext 
            h2 Pilot Data
            p Participating students can view their live responses by loggin in the Ohmage system. There is also a public demo dataset available that was collected during the first pilot study. 
                          
            p During the first pilot study, approximately 2500 survey responses were uploaded. 
              | For the public demo dataset, only complete responses (including photo and GPS location) were included, resulting in a dataset of approx 1700 records.
              | Also, up to 1 mile of noise added to each GPS location that was recorded from the students home to ensure students privacy.
              
            p The raw dataset can be seen  
              a(href="data/demo/snack.csv") here
              |  in CSV format. Please do not reuse this data for other purposes without permission.
              
          .span4
            h2 The Dashboard
            p The interactive dashboard was developed to visually explore the data. There is both a live version that
              | participating students can use to view each others data, as well as a public static version with a fixed dataset.
              
            p Some of the libraries that are used by the dashboard:  
            ul
              li
                a(href="http://leafletjs.com/") Leaflet
              li
                a(href="http://d3js.org/") D3
              li
                a(href="http://www.jasondavies.com/wordcloud") D3-cloud
              li
                a(href="http://square.github.com/crossfilter/") Crossfilter
              li
                a(href="http://nickqizhu.github.com/dc.js/") dc.js
              li
                a(href="http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/") Twitter Bootstrap
              li
                a(href="http://jqueryui.com/") jQuery{ui}  
             
             p For further questions about the dashboard, contact <a href="http://jeroenooms.github.com">the author</a>.                                                                             
                              
          
